net.joala.data.random

Interface RandomNumberProvider<T extends Comparable<? extends Number>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataProvider<T>, RandomDataProvider<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRandomNumberProvider, RandomDoubleProvider, RandomFloatProvider, RandomIntegerProvider, RandomLongProvider

    public interface RandomNumberProvider<T extends Comparable<? extends Number>>
extends RandomDataProvider<T>

    Provides random numbers. Configuration methods always return self-references.
